<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 22:06:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙边境的以色列军队观察员：“他们拍摄了我们的相机，我们什么也看不见”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-spotter-on-gaza-border-they-shot-our-cameras-we-couldnt-see-a-thing/0000018b-1b64-df31-a99f-7fe7fb600000</link><description>在一份录制的证词中，一名士兵讲述了她和她的朋友们如何在外面的恐怖分子试图闯入的情况下躲藏了几个小时。据她说，观察系统遭到枪击并被禁用，以防止它们被发现</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 21:05:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-spotter-on-gaza-border-they-shot-our-cameras-we-couldnt-see-a-thing/0000018b-1b64-df31-a99f-7fe7fb600000</guid></item><item><title>“真正的灵魂伴侣”在加沙附近的战场上被哈马斯枪杀——他们的家人忙着寻找答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/true-soulmates-shot-by-hamas-near-gaza-and-family-must-scrambles-for-answers/0000018b-1f4e-d465-abbb-1ffedef00000</link><description>朱迪思·韦恩斯坦·哈盖 (Judith Weinstein Haggai) 打电话说，周六早上，她和她的丈夫在基布兹附近遭到枪击。接下来发生的事情尚不清楚——他们的孩子一直在向当局寻求帮助</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 20:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/true-soulmates-shot-by-hamas-near-gaza-and-family-must-scrambles-for-answers/0000018b-1f4e-d465-abbb-1ffedef00000</guid></item><item><title>拜登向以色列人发表了内塔尼亚胡永远无法发表的演讲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.highlight/biden-gave-israelis-the-speech-that-netanyahu-could-never-deliver/0000018b-1f8d-df31-a99f-7fcf0a580001</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登发表了热情洋溢、鼓舞士气的犹太复国主义演讲，而以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡却无法向他心烦意乱的国家发表这样的演讲。但这并不是给以色列政府的空白支票</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 19:22:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.highlight/biden-gave-israelis-the-speech-that-netanyahu-could-never-deliver/0000018b-1f8d-df31-a99f-7fcf0a580001</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦卫生部：3名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸村庄被蒙面定居者杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-3-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-village-by-masked-settlers/0000018b-1f43-df31-a99f-7fc316c90000</link><description>巴勒斯坦卫生部表示，另有八人受伤，被送往萨拉菲特和纳布卢斯的医院，并补充说，其中三人颈部和腹部有枪伤，情况危急</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 16:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-3-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-village-by-masked-settlers/0000018b-1f43-df31-a99f-7fc316c90000</guid></item><item><title>将战争引向哈马斯：决定以色列反应的三个关键因素</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/taking-the-war-to-hamas-three-key-factors-shaping-israels-response/0000018b-1f20-d465-abbb-1fb6e01f0000</link><description>如果政治领导人不明确目标是什么，即使是最周密的计划也会立即出错。这只是第一个问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 15:39:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/taking-the-war-to-hamas-three-key-factors-shaping-israels-response/0000018b-1f20-d465-abbb-1fb6e01f0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦能源局称加沙发电厂因缺乏燃料而停止运营</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/gaza-power-plant-stops-operating-due-to-lack-of-fuel-palestinian-energy-authority-says/0000018b-1efe-d2fc-a59f-dfff86f70000</link><description>巴勒斯坦能源管理局负责人表示，加沙燃料供应的终止是一场“灾难”，可能会产生“广泛的后果”，包括停止供水，将使医院的“恶劣条件”恶化</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 14:50:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/gaza-power-plant-stops-operating-due-to-lack-of-fuel-palestinian-energy-authority-says/0000018b-1efe-d2fc-a59f-dfff86f70000</guid></item><item><title>左翼分子怎么能将哈马斯针对以色列人的暴行称为“巴勒斯坦抵抗”？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-can-left-wingers-hail-hamas-atrocities-against-israelis-as-palestinian-resistance/0000018b-1e0b-df31-a99f-7fcb56df0000</link><description>尽管哈马斯恐怖分子对以色列人进行了伊斯兰国式的屠杀，并将老人、妇女、儿童甚至婴儿绑架到加沙，但左翼的一大派别却忙着支持他们的野蛮行为</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 14:37:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-can-left-wingers-hail-hamas-atrocities-against-israelis-as-palestinian-resistance/0000018b-1e0b-df31-a99f-7fcb56df0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列紧急政府将成立特别战争内阁应对哈马斯战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-gantz-agree-on-formation-of-emergency-govt-during-war-with-hamas/0000018b-1efe-d2fc-a59f-dfffa9fe0000</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡、国防部长约阿夫·加兰特和曾担任以色列国防军参谋长和国防部长的本尼·甘茨将组建紧急政府并领导战时内阁。战略事务部长 Ron Dermer 和 MK Gadi Eisenkot 将担任观察员</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 14:34:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-gantz-agree-on-formation-of-emergency-govt-during-war-with-hamas/0000018b-1efe-d2fc-a59f-dfffa9fe0000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙，“我认为，出于恐惧，很难继续站起来”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/in-gaza-its-hard-to-keep-standing-on-your-feet-out-of-fear-i-think/0000018b-1de0-d465-abbb-1df67d5a0000</link><description>这些评论是来自加沙城的 30 岁律师拉纳（化名）于周二下午发表的，她描述了她经历的第四次或第五次战争（谁能追踪？）</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 14:04:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/in-gaza-its-hard-to-keep-standing-on-your-feet-out-of-fear-i-think/0000018b-1de0-d465-abbb-1df67d5a0000</guid></item><item><title>滞留在雅典：以色列人正在尽一切努力回家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/stranded-in-athens-israelis-are-doing-everything-they-can-to-get-home/0000018b-1ea1-df31-a99f-7fe36e3d0000</link><description>以色列航空公司从该市运营救援航班，导致来自世界各地的以色列人聚集在那里。办理登机手续时，数百名忧心忡忡的以色列人聚集在一起，与家人团聚或加入以色列国防军预备役部队</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 13:46:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/stranded-in-athens-israelis-are-doing-everything-they-can-to-get-home/0000018b-1ea1-df31-a99f-7fe36e3d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总理本-格维尔：从现在起，南部城市斯德洛特的每个居民都可以携带武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-ben-gvir-from-now-on-every-resident-of-southern-city-sderot-can-bear-arms/0000018b-1e29-d47b-a7fb-bff927e10000</link><description>哈马斯突然渗透以色列后，以色列国家安全部长表示，这场战争证明我们需要武装我们的公民</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 12:52:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-ben-gvir-from-now-on-every-resident-of-southern-city-sderot-can-bear-arms/0000018b-1e29-d47b-a7fb-bff927e10000</guid></item><item><title>帮助拯救基布兹的以色列妇女：“我不是英雄，我不是一个人在那里”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-woman-who-helped-save-a-kibbutz-im-not-a-hero-i-wasnt-there-by-myself/0000018b-1e4f-d47b-a7fb-bfdf2e560000</link><description>不到一年前，当 Inbal Lieberman 首次担任 Nir ​​Am 安全协调员时，她被告知：“我希望你不要有太多事情要做。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 12:44:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-woman-who-helped-save-a-kibbutz-im-not-a-hero-i-wasnt-there-by-myself/0000018b-1e4f-d47b-a7fb-bfdf2e560000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡为何要加强哈马斯？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-needed-a-strong-hamas/0000018b-1e9f-d47b-a7fb-bfdfd8f30000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 12:28:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-needed-a-strong-hamas/0000018b-1e9f-d47b-a7fb-bfdfd8f30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人即使热血沸腾也必须保持人性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-must-maintain-their-humanity-even-when-their-blood-boils/0000018b-1e18-d465-abbb-1ebe62c80000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 11:57:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-must-maintain-their-humanity-even-when-their-blood-boils/0000018b-1e18-d465-abbb-1ebe62c80000</guid></item><item><title>超过一万名美国犹太人在联合国前集会表达对以色列的声援</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/more-than-10-000-american-jews-express-solidarity-with-israel-at-rally-in-front-of-un/0000018b-1c9e-d08b-adef-1ffe20850000</link><description>这是自周六上午战争爆发以来为支持以色列举行的最大规模的国际集会，也是几十年来首次将如此大规模的美国犹太人聚集在一起</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 11:35:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/more-than-10-000-american-jews-express-solidarity-with-israel-at-rally-in-front-of-un/0000018b-1c9e-d08b-adef-1ffe20850000</guid></item><item><title>自哈马斯袭击以色列以来，法国报告了数十起反犹太主义行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-11/ty-article/france-reports-dozens-of-antisemitic-acts-since-hamas-attack-on-israel/0000018b-1e40-d465-abbb-1ef6cceb0000</link><description>法国教育部长称，巴黎大区一名犹太学生遭到同学袭击，撕破了他的 T 恤</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 10:54:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-11/ty-article/france-reports-dozens-of-antisemitic-acts-since-hamas-attack-on-israel/0000018b-1e40-d465-abbb-1ef6cceb0000</guid></item><item><title>如何与您的孩子谈论以色列-加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/how-to-talk-to-your-children-about-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-1b54-df31-a99f-7fd7f1430000</link><description>我们都在尽最大努力保护我们的孩子免受新闻和互联网上可怕的可怕图像的影响，但我们需要明白，即使是很小的孩子也能敏锐地意识到周围发生的事情。以下是有关如何解决这种情况的一些实用建议</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 10:45:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/how-to-talk-to-your-children-about-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-1b54-df31-a99f-7fd7f1430000</guid></item><item><title>“不是以色列国防军，不是警察。一块金属在纳哈尔奥兹救了我、我的妻子和我们的孩子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/not-the-idf-not-the-police-what-saved-my-family-in-nahal-oz-was-a-piece-of-metal/0000018b-1d7a-d2fc-a59f-dd7b0d5a0000</link><description>在大屠杀发生很久之后，数百名从纳哈尔奥兹基布兹获救的以色列人描述了恐惧，以及被遗弃的感觉。但他们想回家</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 09:36:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/not-the-idf-not-the-police-what-saved-my-family-in-nahal-oz-was-a-piece-of-metal/0000018b-1d7a-d2fc-a59f-dd7b0d5a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列援助组织将创伤专业知识带回家乡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/bringing-trauma-expertise-full-circle-back-to-israel/0000018b-1d9d-d465-abbb-1dbfea960000</link><description>以色列援助团体帮助了世界各地偏远地区的灾难受害者，但现在，他们正在离家更近的地方运用他们的技能</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 08:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/bringing-trauma-expertise-full-circle-back-to-israel/0000018b-1d9d-d465-abbb-1dbfea960000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡推迟与甘茨就紧急战时政府问题举行会晤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-postpones-meeting-with-gantz-over-emergency-wartime-government/0000018b-1d9a-d465-abbb-1dbeac090000</link><description>两人定于周三会面。民族团结党消息人士称：“内塔尼亚胡正在拖延、拖延、拖延。首相没有表现出任何惊慌的迹象”</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 07:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-postpones-meeting-with-gantz-over-emergency-wartime-government/0000018b-1d9a-d465-abbb-1dbea